      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature succeeded, but didn't critically succeed, at a Perception check or Will save to disbelieve an illusion from a spell that you cast.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are within 30 feet of the observer and the illusion.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You use your deceptive skills to make your illusions seem even more real. Attempt a @Check[type:deception|defense:perception] check against the target's Perception DC. If you succeed, the target fails to disbelieve the illusion.</p>"
